equipa.guilherme_vieira.bio:
Twenty-one years of experience in national and multinational companies in the Information and Communication Technology (ICT) sector, eighteen of which supporting organizational changes involving complex business processes; 



 Solid commercial and business development experience gained through extensive engagement in negotiating ICT solutions (software, hardware, and services) across the Southeast, Northeast, South, and Central-West regions of Brazil;

Consistent performance and knowledge in all phases of the sales cycle for public and private organizations.
